## Notes for Using with Copilot:
- Complete each phase in order
- Test thoroughly before moving to next phase
- Take breaks between major phases
- Document any deviations or custom solutions
- Keep Git commits aligned with phase completions
- Reference this checklist in prompts: "I'm working on Phase X: [Phase Name]"